equals(name)) {\n                return new ByteArrayInputStream(classBytes);\n            }\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        private List<String> resourceRequests() {\n            return resourceRequests;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777439726026}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_8Wsf8AuXWOmBNlbRQLOVAzgp|fc_046ae75d20ac57fc0169f193eda2008194acf5f227b6efc2c8", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "?? tests/src/org.aspectj/aspectjweaver/1.9.7/src/test/java/org_aspectj/aspectjweaver/NonCachingClassLoaderRepositoryTest.java\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777439726126}]}
